 bin Mansor</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Ts. Tarmimi bin Sahad</li><li class=\"ql-align-justify\">Mazlina binti Yusoff</li></ul><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Asia-Pacific Broadcasting Union (ABU)</p>','2024-10-27 22:24:00','2024-10-27 22:24:07',445,446,NULL),(229,1,184,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730096744-1729474281-istanbulabu1.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730096744-1729474281-istanbulabu1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730096770-1729474331-istanbulabu2.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730096770-1729474331-istanbulabu2.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730096799-1729474370-istanbulabu3.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730096799-1729474370-istanbulabu3.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 22:24:49','2024-10-27 22:27:34',447,448,NULL),(230,1,186,'HTML','<p>Tahniah Selamat Pagi Malaysia (SPM) atas anugerah ‘Program Wacana Terbaik’ oleh UKM di Majlis MediaWave UKM 2024</p>','2024-10-27 22:43:32','2024-10-27 22:43:32',449,450,NULL),(231,1,186,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730097849-1726712483-mediawaveukm242.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730097849-1726712483-mediawaveukm242.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730097874-1726712516-mediawaveukm243.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730097874-1726712516-mediawaveukm243.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\"