lam Malaysia Book Of Records. Tahniah Radio RTM , 33 stesen 1 Suara.</p>','2024-10-27 23:01:52','2024-10-27 23:01:52',457,458,NULL),(235,1,188,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730098952-1725939901-largestmerdekababies1.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730098952-1725939901-largestmerdekababies1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730098957-1725939901-largestmerdekababies2.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730098957-1725939901-largestmerdekababies2.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730098961-1725940039-largestmerdekababies3.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730098961-1725940039-largestmerdekababies3.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:01:55','2024-10-27 23:03:15',459,460,NULL),(236,1,189,'HTML','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">RTM Perak cemerlang meraih empat anugerah dalam Majlis Anugerah Media Majlis Bandaraya Ipoh (MBI) 2024.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Anugerah yang julung kali diadakan itu bertujuan mengiktiraf peranan dan sumbangan media dalam menyampaikan maklumat yang tepat dan sahih berkaitan MBI.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Wartawan RTM Perak Nor Ain Abu Bakar dipilih sebagai Wartawan Terbaik hasil beberapa pencapaian yang diraih sepanjang tahun lalu.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Antaranya pemenang tempat pertama Anugerah Liputan Kemampanan Persekitaran Hijau Terbaik, Kementerian Perumahan dan Kerajaan Tempatan (KPKT) 2023.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Nor Ain turut merangkul Anugerah Laporan Berita TV Terbaik menerusi laporan ‘MBI Kitar Minyak Terpakai’.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Anugerah Laporan Khas TV Terbaik pula disampaikan kepada Amirul Ashraff Zainon menerusi laporan khas \'Anjing Dalam Distress\'.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Manakala, Mohd Ariff Kamalzee Harun dipilih sebagai Juruvideo Terbaik menerusi laporan berita \'Smart Traffic\'.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Datuk Bandar Ipoh, Datuk Rumaizi Baharin hadir pada majlis tersebut selain kehadiran hampir 500 tetamu terdiri daripada pengamal media pelbagai agensi dan kakitangan MBI.</p><p><br></p>','2024-10-27 23:04:45','2024-10-27 23:04:45',461,462,NULL),(237,1,189,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099115-1723515531-whatsapp-image-2024-08-11-at-110041-pm-1.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099115-1723515531-whatsapp-image-2024-08-11-at-110041-pm-1.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099118-1723515556-whatsapp-image-2024-08-11-at-110041-pm.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099118-1723515556-whatsapp-image-2024-08-11-at-110041-pm.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099122-1723515584-whatsapp-image-2024-08-11-at-110041-pm-2.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099122-1723515584-whatsapp-image-2024-08-11-at-110041-pm-2.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:04:53','2024-10-27 23:06:03',463,464,NULL),(238,1,190,'HTML','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Setinggi-tinggi tahniah diucapkan kepada Radio Televisyen Malaysia yang memenangi&nbsp;<strong>Anugerah Khas Kepimpinan Perdana Universiti Awam Malaysia - Agensi Penyiaran Berita (Kerajaan Persekutuan) Paling Popular Di Universiti Awam</strong>&nbsp;dalam&nbsp;<strong>Anugerah Pentadbir Gemilang Universiti Awam Malaysia 2024 sempena Sambutan Hari Pentadbir Universiti Awam Malaysia 2024.</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Syabas diucapkan!</p><p><br></p>','2024-10-27 23:14:27','2024-10-27 23:14:27',465,466,NULL),(239,1,190,'HTML','<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099698-1724210392-anugerakhaskepimpinanperdana.png\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099698-1724210392-anugerakhaskepimpinanperdana.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>','2024-10-27 23:14:45','2024-10-27 23:15:07',467,468,NULL),(240,1,191,'HTML','<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099777-1723082423-ispms.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099777-1723082423-ispms.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>','2024-10-27 23:16:04','2024-10-27 23:16:27',471,472,NULL),(241,1,191,'HTML','<p>Alhamdulillah, RTM telah menerima Sijil Apresiasi ISPMS daripada pihak Cybersecurity Malaysia sempena Pameran CyberDSA 2024 @ KLCC. Tahniah</p>','2024-10-27 23:16:41','2024-10-27 23:16:43',469,470,NULL),(242,1,192,'HTML','<p>Asiavision Award</p>','2024-10-27 23:17:16','2024-10-27 23:17:16',473,474,NULL),(243,1,192,'HTML','<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099858-1721804785-asiavisionaward.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099858-1721804785-asiavisionaward.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>','2024-10-27 23:17:29','2024-10-27 23:17:48',475,476,NULL),(244,1,193,'HTML','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Tahniah!</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pemenang Hadiah Kewartawanan Malaysia MPI- PETRONAS 2023 (HKM 2023)</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Malaysia MADANI : Tekad Perpaduan Penuhi Harapan</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">\'Yang sahih di Berita RTM\'</p><p><br></p>','2024-10-27 23:19:25','2024-10-27 23:19:25',477,478,NULL),(245,1,193,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099991-1717984206-mpipetronas1.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099991-1717984206-mpipetronas1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099999-1717984231-mpipetronas2.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730099999-1717984231-mpipetronas2.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100003-1718001812-mpipemenangsemua.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100003-1718001812-mpipemenangsemua.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:19:28','2024-10-27 23:20:38',479,480,NULL),(246,1,194,'HTML','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Enam pengamal media dari Radio Televisyen Malaysia (RTM) mendapat pengiktirafan dalam Anugerah Media Agrobank 2023/2024 menerusi menerbitkan liputan media yang positif, tepat dan holistik berkaitan aktiviti pertanian dan keselamatan makanan.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Juara kategori Anugerah Media Penyiaran Televisyen &amp; Video Dalam Talian (Berita Terbaik) dirangkul oleh Nurfatihah Ab Rahim dari RTM Kuala Lumpur (KL) dalam pelaporan bertajuk \'Agrobank Prihatin Tingkat Sosioekonomi Rakyat Menerusi Program Agro Komuniti B40\', manakala Zakiyamani Ahmad (RTM Perlis) tempat ketiga menerusi \'Bakti Pesawah Muda - Bangga Bantu Jamin Bekalan Makanan Negara Biarpun Berhimpit Cabaran\'.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Sementara itu, Anugerah Media Penyiaran Televisyen &amp; Video Dalam Talian (Dokumentari Terbaik) diumumkan juara bagi Azry Ahmad Mustafa Hadi (RTM KL) - laporan bertajuk \'Agrotek: Kemahuan Tonggak Kejayaan\', manakala naib juara oleh Alya Alvian Washif dari RTM Sabah - \'Surupu Mutanom Punti\'.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Seterusnya juara bagi kategori Anugerah Media Radio Terbaik dinobat kepada Paranthaman a/l Nadarajan (Perak FM) menerusi segmen \'Pertanian Bandar\', manakala Hafizah Rosli (Mutiara FM) di tempat ketiga - \'Sembang Luaq Konti - Jom Agro (Ikan Keli Pejal)\'.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Tahniah diucapkan kepada semua pemenang. Majlis ini dianjurkan oleh Agrobank dan Malaysia Press Institute (MPI).</p><p><br></p>','2024-10-27 23:21:20','2024-10-27 23:21:20',481,482,NULL),(247,1,194,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100104-1717040535-3005-anugerah-media-agrobank.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100104-1717040535-3005-anugerah-media-agrobank.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100110-1717040561-3005-anugerah-media-agrobank-3.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100110-1717040561-3005-anugerah-media-agrobank-3.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:21:27','2024-10-27 23:22:17',483,484,NULL),(248,1,195,'HTML','<p>Ucapan terima kasih dan penghargaan China Media Group kepada RTM atas kerjasama penerbitan dokumentari khas cerita kita sempena ulangtahun ke 50 hubungan diplomatik negara Malaysia dan China</p>','2024-10-27 23:24:36','2024-10-27 23:24:36',485,486,NULL),(249,1,195,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100306-1714465884-surat1.png\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100306-1714465884-surat1.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100310-1714465909-surat2.png\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100310-1714465909-surat2.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100314-1714465935-ucapanterimakasihkepadakprtm.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100314-1714465935-ucapanterimakasihkepadakprtm.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:24:44','2024-10-27 23:25:49',487,488,NULL),(250,1,196,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100454-1709517190-mfmpa1.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100454-1709517190-mfmpa1.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100459-1709517216-mfpma2.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100459-1709517216-mfpma2.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:27:21','2024-10-27 23:28:02',489,490,NULL),(251,1,197,'HTML','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Syabas dan Tahniah kepada team produksi Pekan Kecil Kampung Terpencil. Unit Drama RTM (Official) telah menerima 5 anugerah terbaik dalam Anugerah Telenovela 9.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Drama terbaik Anugerah Telenovela</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pengarah Drama Terbaik Wan Afzam Wan Daud</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Penulis Skrip Terbaik</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Penyunting Terbaik Izhar Masuri</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Pengarah Seni Terbaik Radzuan Romli</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Terima Kasih kepada seluruh team, crew produksi PKKT, para pelakon, penduduk Kampung Sungai Lembing, Dewan Bahasa Dan Pustaka #DBP dan kepada yang menjayakan Drama 10 episod Pekan Kecil Kampung Terpencil.</p><p><br></p>','2024-10-27 23:29:14','2024-10-27 23:29:14',491,492,NULL),(252,1,197,'HTML','<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100609-1708930085-anugerahtelonovela2411.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100570-1708930085-anugerahtelonovela2411.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100574-1708930112-anugerahtelonovela242.jpeg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100574-1708930112-anugerahtelonovela242.jpeg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>\r\n	</div>	\r\n	\r\n		</div>','2024-10-27 23:29:18','2024-10-27 23:30:22',493,494,NULL),(253,1,198,'HTML','<a href=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100800-theyvekgan.jpg\"><img src=\"/storage/article_assets/1730100800-theyvekgan.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a>','2024-10-27 23:33:04','2024-10-27 23:33:33',495,496,NULL),(255,1,200,'HTML','<p>Ayam</p>','2024-11-26 22:47:47','2024-11-26 22:47:47',497,498,NULL);
